rld\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her body has been battered and restored, her spirit treated the same by the sport she has alternatively loved and detested in equal measure.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her body\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"her spirit\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"equal measure\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she has emerged on the other side as something more than just a wizened athlete; she has come into her full self.\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the other side\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"just a wizened athlete\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"her full self\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My motto these last two months is 'I am that girl,'\\\" Chiles says.\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My motto\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"these last two months\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"that girl\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have nothing to prove to anyone.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about myself.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have nothing to prove, but I believe I have more to give.\\\"\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1602}]}, {\"sentence\":