\": 5443, \"to\": 5457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The irony is that collegiate gymnasts compete more - there are meets nearly every weekend - and yet as the demands increased, Chiles made a blissful discovery.\", \"from\": 5460, \"to\": 5619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The irony\", \"from\": 5460, \"to\": 5469}, {\"ngram\": \"collegiate gymnasts\", \"from\": 5478, \"to\": 5497}, {\"ngram\": \"the demands\", \"from\": 5563, \"to\": 5574}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5592}, {\"ngram\": \"a blissful discovery\", \"from\": 5598, \"to\": 5618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her life did not have to be an either/or.\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her life\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5628}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My sport and my life can be separate,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 5663, \"to\": 5712, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My sport\", \"from\": 5664, \"to\": 5672}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can have fun within my sport and outside of it as well.\", \"from\": 5713, \"to\": 5771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5728}, {\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 5736, \"to\": 5744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not everything has to be about my sport.\\\"\", \"from\": 5772, \"to\": 5813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not everything\", \"from\": 5772, \"to\": 5786}, {\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 5803, \"to\": 5811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That, of course, becomes a far more difficult pursuit when the dangling carrot is a spot on the Olympic team.\", \"from\": 5815, \"to\": 5924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 5824, \"to\": 5830}, {\"ngram\": \"a far more difficult pursuit\", \"from\": 5840, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"the dangling carrot\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 5893}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 5897, \"to\": 5903}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team\", \"from\": 5907, \"to\": 5923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is, currently, all about the sport, and Chiles' epiphany should not be misconstrued as a de-emphasis on competitiveness.\", \"from\": 5925, \"to\": 6048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5953, \"to\": 5962}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles' epiphany\", \"from\": 5968, \"to\": 5984}, {\"ngram\": \"a de\", \"from\": 6015, \"to\": 6019}, {\"ngram\": \"emphasis\", \"from\": 6020, \"to\": 6028}, {\"ngram\": \"competitiveness\", \"from\": 6032, \"to\": 6047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once her shoulder injury is mended, she has every intention of approaching her training with the same gusto she always has and setting the same standard of excellence.\", \"from\": 6049, \"to\": 6216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her shoulder injury\", \"from\": 6054, \"to\": 6073}, {\"ngram\": \"every intention\", \"from\": 6093, \"to\": 6108}, {\"ngram\": \"her training\", \"from\": 6124, \"to\": 6136}, {\"ngram\": \"the same gusto\", \"from\": 6142, \"to\": 6156}, {\"ngram\": \"the same standard\", \"from\": 6184, \"to\": 6201}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 6205, \"to\": 6215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That, Chiles says, needs to be clear.\", \"from\": 6217, \"to\": 6254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 6223, \"to\": 6229}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not come back to put on a face,\\\" she says.\", \"from\": 6256, \"to\": 6305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a face\", \"from\": 6287, \"to\": 6293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I came back because I have more to give.\\\"\", \"from\": 6306, \"to\": 6348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At various times in her career, Chiles has carried the torch as a Black woman and powerful athlete in a sport that lacked color and favored litheness.\", \"from\": 6350, \"to\": 6500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"various times